modName: Thieves Guild door and Fast Travel
summary: Allows you to fast travel from the Ragged Flagon and adds a trapdoor into the Flagon.
descriptionHtml: I got sick of constantly running to and from the Flagon during the Thieves Guild quests so I made this. Allows you to fast travel out from the Ragged Flagon and adds a trapdoor just outside the secret entrance in the graveyard where the thieves guild map marker is which leads straight into the Flagon, allowing you to bypass the central cistern room.
author: Drakynval
